    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of uv_build</title>

      <para>
        Build the module:
      </para>

&build-wheel;

      <para>
        This package does not come with a test suite.
      </para>

      <para>
        Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>&install-wheel; uv_build</userinput></screen>

